--><br /><nowiki>! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | [[Academy Award for Best Director|Best Director]]</nowiki><!--
--><br /><nowiki>|-</nowiki><!--
--><br /><nowiki>| style="vertical-align:top;" |</nowiki><!--
--><br /><nowiki>... (nominees/award for 1st category)</nowiki><!--
--><br /><nowiki>| style="vertical-align:top;" |</nowiki><!--
--><br /><nowiki>... (nominees/award for 2nd category)</nowiki></code><!--
--><br />
